OL,5, A couple say they are "fighting to     
OL,6, survive" due to the increasing cost of 
OL,7, energy.                                
OL,9,FStacey McDonnell and Darren Setford    
OL,10,Flive in Leicester and are full-time    
OL,11,Fcarers for family members.             
OL,13,FThey say that by the time they have    
OL,14,Fpaid their #700 a month rent, there is 
OL,15,Fnot a lot to spare.                    
OL,17,FThe Clockwise Credit Union, which      
OL,18,Fprovides support to people struggling  
OL,19,Fto manage their finances, has advised  
OL,20,Fstruggling families to ask for help.   
